  "texts": [
    "In this section, we propose a categorization, based on the features used by the existing methods.",
    "Each method is categorized based on the primary feature it focuses on.",
    "In general, there are two approaches to combat disinformation: intervention and detection.",
    "The primary objective of detection approaches is to identify and distinguish disinformation from true information.",
    "On the other hand, the goal of intervention approaches is to impede the dissemination and spread of disinformation."
